    "Distribution of positive and negative classifications in five benchmark PPI corpora.",
    "Dataset Positive Negative Unique Sentences BioInfer 2534 7132 1100 IEPA 335 482 486 HPRD50 163 270 145 LLL 164 166 77 https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0303231.t002",
